<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Pfalz-Neumarkt</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Unterstützung wegen Herausgabe der von Amtleuten des Adressaten beschlagnahmten Erbschaft der Petersen Entenberger von ihrer verstorbenen Muhme N. Mayr von Lieritzhofen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_374" id="186r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_374_r1l15">Hercʒog <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_374_r1l16">Gnediger herre Vns <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> . S . <expan>Entemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l17">vnd Peters ſein elıche <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan> . vvie 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ </del> Jr mume dy </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l18"><expan>Maẏerin<ex>n</ex></expan> von lernſhofen nu von tods wegen <expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l19">vnd etvvieuil habe vnd beſunder etvvaʒ parſchaft gelaſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l20">die ſie <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ır<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>mume<ex>n</ex></expan> peterſen gemainet vnd ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l21">ſchickt hab . vnd auch der nehſter erb ſeẏ / daran ſie etlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l22">ewr Amptlewte 
<del rend="strikethrough">n </del> engen . vnd ſich der <expan>vntervvunde<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l23">als ſie <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden das ſelber auch wol <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vverde<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l24"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr <expan>de<ex>m</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> wirtin ewr gnedig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l25"><expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darynne geruchet cʒu beweiſen / daʒ Jn dieſelb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l26">Jr habe darcʒu ſie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> reht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vngehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> volge oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_374_r1l27"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> ſlewnig reht wıderfare Als etc das <expan>vvolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_374" id="186r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger herre, uns <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">S.</expan>
<expan>Entemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, und Peters sein
                                                eliche <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie ir mume,
                                                dy <expan>Mayerin<ex>n</ex></expan> von Lernshofen,
                                                nu von tods wegen <expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                                sey und etwievil habe und besunder etwaz parschaft
                                                gelassen, die sie <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>mume<ex>n</ex></expan> Petersen gemainet und
                                                geschickt hab und auch der nehster erb sey, daran
                                                sie etlich ewr amptlewte engen und sich der
                                                  <expan>unterwunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als sie
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden das selber
                                                auch wol <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> wirtin ewr gnedig
                                                  <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darynne geruchet
                                                czu beweisen, daz in dieselb ir habe, darczu sie
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> reht
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                                  <expan>ungehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> volge oder
                                                  <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> slewnig reht
                                                widerfare. Als etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
